comment: Davis (POR) attempts to get in path of Smith (PHI), who avoids the screen.
Thompson (PHI) dislodges Harkless (POR), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Aminu (POR) makes incidental contact with Thompson (PHI) prior to the inbound.
Covington (PHI) splits his feet on the perimeter.
Davis (POR) makes contact with Covington (PHI) that affects his shot attempt.
Stauskas (PHI) makes contact with Harkless's (POR) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Davis (POR) maintains legal guarding position with Grant (PHI) and cleanly blocks his shot.
[Observable in enhanced video] McCollum (POR) maintains his pivot foot during tight double team, briefly losing control of the ball as he starts the dribble.
Covington (PHI) makes contact with McCollum's (POR) arms that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Grant (PHI).
Grant (PHI) commits a lane violation. The free throw shooter may not step over the plane of the free throw line until the ball touches the basket ring, backboard or the free throw ends.
Covington (PHI) makes incidental contact with McCollum (POR) that does not affect his RSBQ.
